{"tid":2331953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北韓船長偷聽《自由亞洲電台》 當100人面前被處決","createTime":"2020-12-19T08:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T01:13:49.000Z","uid":66271,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d776d4fdd94d3c12f779db844546971370849247","tid":2331953,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/12/18/phpv1nASZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F12%2F18%2Fphpv1nASZ.jpg&h=d955bdca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北韓1名漁船船長被政府發現長期收聽《自由亞洲電台》廣播，被認定企圖顛覆朝鮮勞動黨，在100名船長與漁業高層面前被公開處決，咸鏡北道的執法人員已經確認這項消息。<br />\n<br />\n根據《自由亞洲電台》報導，被處死的崔姓船長享年40多歲，他效力於北韓中央附屬漁業基地，過去曾在北韓軍隊擔任上尉，負責50多條船組成的船隊，卻因傲慢無禮而惹怒漁民，將他在船上收聽《自由亞洲電台》朝鮮語節目的事件報告給安全部門，全案因此曝光。<br />\n<br />\n崔男被捕後，坦言從24歲起就一直收聽《自由亞洲電台》，當時他是1名無線電廣播員，退伍後繼續收聽是為了回味軍中記憶；船員們則指稱，崔男在遠洋捕魚時，固定不斷收聽外國廣播；消息人士指出，咸鏡北道安全部門以企圖顛覆勞動黨罪名將他處決，同時解散了允許崔男在海上工作的官員。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士透露，「眾所周知，北韓軍事無線電運營商和漁民經常收聽《自由亞洲電台》」，但現在北韓政府透過崔姓船長殺雞儆猴，給北韓民眾們留下的深刻印象是：收聽外國廣播電台意味著死亡。"},{"pid":"5c9bd92d5fccc266741e6054d0bf5673da1c3fc2","tid":2331953,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c8c797f2a3eecf5a29347a6b87a579a707a5dd","tid":2331953,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d501e4f6c566713a4a70149a9726bf62d447794","tid":2331953,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1a4fcb5195c7f4e701973b011dbc35e5a8546b","tid":2331953,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:29:12.000Z","msg":"自由亞洲電台<br />\n有AM台"},{"pid":"a7a73c4422b2bef0a77c9fd07deffba6365dc406","tid":2331953,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:29:12.000Z","msg":"自由亞洲電台有講韓語嗎 ?"},{"pid":"a6f20587d38fdc6b65d20e197e1c9d6d8e57917d","tid":2331953,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:29:28.000Z","msg":"好快到香港"},{"pid":"59f1631b275669d94f6be41265bfabb9812338d5","tid":2331953,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404c0f353d35f63332788d82b01f8340419e2d25","tid":2331953,"uid":251732,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a7a73c4422b2bef0a77c9fd07deffba6365dc406","tid":2331953,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:29:12.000Z","msg":"自由亞洲電台有講韓語嗎 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:30:14.000Z","msg":"有， 自由亞洲電台有放唔同語言比亞洲各地嘅人"},{"pid":"2f10108d3ecb59f366cd0e37ee30b35e884f2274","tid":2331953,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:31:33.000Z","msg":"癲"},{"pid":"14c0a7b40b516c2f5cc78f1f9cac015f460125b6","tid":2331953,"uid":37389,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"出賣佢嗰班人好快會一齊消失，知船長有聽即係佢哋偷聽船長聽緊乜，即係佢哋都聽到廣播內容啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cefe69e51091a4ab05ff59082856e1b21ac8f242","tid":2331953